Who the hell are you?! How did you get here?!

It's none of your business. I'm going to set free
the loli-mon over there.

Hahaha, you're really something, jumping from the
frying pan into the fire! Not only do you have a
loli-mon with you, but a magical girl too. You're
quite lucky!

You won't understand until you experience pain.
Make sure you don't regret it.

You're just weak. Here's the key, let's help them,

Ugh... I let my guard down...

Uhyaa! You're so weak! Where did that confidence
from earlier go?

Are you okay? Everyone still feels even more
childish than before, don't you think?

We're still apprentice Lolimon, you know? We were
taking on trials in Marimari-sama's Trial Corridor
when we got captured by Bandits...

Is that so?! How did we end up getting captured in
a place like this...

The nearby water source has a deep area that
connects to a cave-like Trial Corridor. It seems
that the bandits invaded from there...

I'm glad you're safe. Let's escape from here and
return to the Village of Divine Trees. There's no
one else here, right?

We were imprisoned here, but Rudia-sama was taken
to a different place.

Yeah. Rudia-sama protected us until the end, but
she was defeated by the bandits...

Alright, I understand. For now, let's quickly get
away from here. Our comrades might come. I'll
explain this to Demetri when I return, so it's
better to let him know about this.
Alright! Big sister, be careful too!

I'm glad we're safe. We can return to the Trial
Corridor from the water source over there.

Is it the messenger of Big Sister Marimari-sama, I
wonder?
That's right. I was asked to rescue all of you.

I see, but we were imprisoned here, while Rudia-
sama was taken to a different place.

Yeah, Lady Rudia protected us until the end, but
she was defeated by the bandits...

I understand. For now, let's quickly get away from
here. Our comrades might come back. I'll explain
this to Demetri when I return, so it's better to
let him know.
Yes! Big Sister, please take care too!
